<?xml version="1.0"?>
<info xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance"
      xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="https://apps.nextcloud.com/schema/apps/info.xsd">
    <id>sharegate</id>
    <name>付费分享</name>
    <summary>付费文件分享 — 公开链接、付费管理、统计与支付宝当面付</summary>
    <description><![CDATA[在 Nextcloud 内为网盘文件创建付费外链，买家支付后下载或转存到本站账户。

**管理台四页**：你的共享（文件表）· 付费分享 · 账户绑定 · 收益查看（预览/转存/下载）

- 支付宝当面付（沙箱/生产）或 Mock 开发支付
- 卖家管理台融入 NC 全局侧栏
- 无需单独部署 ShareGate 服务

兼容 Nextcloud 28–33。
    ]]></description>
    <version>1.3.2</version>
    <licence>agpl</licence>
    <author mail="abitlea@126.com">abitlea</author>
    <namespace>ShareGate</namespace>
    <category>tools</category>
    <website>https://github.com/abitlea/sharegate-nextcloud</website>
    <bugs>https://github.com/abitlea/sharegate-nextcloud/issues</bugs>
    <repository type="git">https://github.com/abitlea/sharegate-nextcloud.git</repository>
    <screenshot small-thumbnail="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/abitlea/sharegate-nextcloud/main/release/screenshots/02-paid-shares.png">https://raw.githubusercontent.com/abitlea/sharegate-nextcloud/main/release/screenshots/01-your-shares.png</screenshot>
